<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <title>404 - Trang không tồn tại | HaziShop</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.3.0/js/all.css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027 0%, #203a43 50%, #2c5364 100%);
            --accent-color: #00d2ff;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .background-blob {
            position: absolute;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 70%);
            z-index: -1;
            filter: blur(50px);
            animation: move 20s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes move {
            from {
                transform: translate(-30%, -30%);
            }

            to {
                transform: translate(30%, 30%);
            }
        }

        .content-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 650px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            position: relative;
        }

        .illustration {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .error-num {
            font-size: 150px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 30%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background: #fff;
            color: #0f2027;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background: #f0f0f0;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #0f2027;
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .icon-box {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            opacity: 0.5;
            animation: float 4s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes float {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-num {
                font-size: 100px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .actions {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .content-card {
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="background-blob"></div>

    <div class="content-card">
        <div class="illustration">
            <div class="icon-box" style="top: -20px; left: 10%;"><i class="fas fa-laptop"></i></div>
            <div class="icon-box" style="bottom: -10px; right: 10%; animation-delay: 2s;"><i class="fas fa-mouse"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="error-num">404</h2>
        </div>

        <h1>Lạc lối giữa rừng công nghệ?</h1>
        <p>Trang bạn đang tìm kiếm đã được nâng cấp hoặc chuyển sang một vũ trụ khác. Hãy để chúng tôi đưa bạn quay lại!
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn-custom btn-primary-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Quay về trang chủ
            </a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-custom btn-secondary-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-undo"></i> Trang trước đó
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Smooth magnetic effect for the card
        const card = document.querySelector('.content-card');
        document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
            const xAxis = (window.innerWidth / 2 - e.pageX) / 50;
            const yAxis = (window.innerHeight / 2 - e.pageY) / 50;
            card.style.transform = `rotateY(${xAxis}px) rotateX(${yAxis}px)`;
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>